Context("Numeric");
#given
$c = random(6,18,.1);


#image scale
$imgScale =0.4;

#image aspect ratio
$width = $imgScale*625;
$height = $imgScale*699;

#computation 
$c56 = 2*$c;
$c24 = 2*$c;
$cx = $c*$c24/($c+$c24)+$c56;
$ceq = $cx*$c/($cx+$c);

#set tolerance
Context()->flags->set(
tolerance=>.01);

##############################################################
#
#  PGML 
#
#

BEGIN_PGML

[@ image( "UBC-CIR-17-018.png", width=>[$width], height=>[$height]) @]*

In the following network, calculate the equivalent capcitance at terminal [`ab`]. Each capacitor is [`[$c]`] [`\mu F`].

[`C_{eq}=`] [_____]{"$ceq"} [`\mu F`]  

END_PGML

